Hey There,

The rank System at our place is pretty simple 

*FLIGHT SCHOOL RANKS* (Times are cumulative)

S1-PPL guidelines operating a single propellor aircraft 
S2-Multi engine rating aswell as Instrument flight rating 
S3-CPL Where the pilot is preparing operations of jet turbine aircraft
S4-ATPL This is the testing stage after which you are cleared to operate for us with passengers

*COMMERCIAL PILOT RANKS*
CHPO -  0hrs (Just cleared Flight school and start with transporting passengers)
CHFO - 10-15hrs 
CHFC - 40-50hrs 
CHC - 65-100hrs
JCFO - 100-125hrs
CMFO - 150-175hrs
CAPT - 200-250hrs
